          { "feature": "onset_years_to_decades_post_treatment", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Baseline and serial echo (LVEF) at 1, 3, 5, and 10 years post-treatment. ACEi + beta-blockers at first sign of LV dysfunction. Dexrazoxane for anthracycline cardioprotection in high dose. Treat risk factors (HTN, DM, dyslipidemia). Lifestyle modification."
      },
      {
